@node "editor" "How to use the editor"
 @{b}The Editor@{ub}

 Using the editor you can edit all the team and driver data
 of the game. Use the left mousebutton to select a button to
 edit.

 When you edit a number, the minimum number you should enter is
 1 and the highest 100.
@endnode

